snippet.title: Tales of Symphonia Remastered | Story Trailer
snippet.description:
Legend says that a Chosen One will one day ascend the Tower of Salvation and save a dying world.

Embark on a journey with Lloyd Irving and friends in Tales of Symphonia Remastered, coming to PS4, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One & Nintendo Switch on Feb. 17, 2023!

Pre-Order: https://bnent.eu/TOSRpreorder

Follow us on:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/talesofseries/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TalesofSeries
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/tales/
Web: https://www.talesofarise.com
